resources.string: "Za a daidaita, hakan kuma zai iya daukar cinkoson netwok mai yawa, a ci gaba a daidaita"
"Faldar da take da alamun hadari za a daidaita, a sake nuna wannan gargadin nan gaba?"
"Za a fara daidata albam ta bayan fage, a iya ci gaab da bincika albam din"
"Babu karamin hot, za a ci gaba da daidaita hotuna daga ma\'ajiyar \'cloud\', a sake nuna wannan gargadin nan gaba?""
"Albam din a ingance yake, babu bukatar wata daidaitawa"
"An daidaita, ga lambobin da aka daidaita"
"Babu netwok, don haka ba a daidaita ba, a kunna netwok"
